metadata.name: Put me in a Frame #36

attributes.trait_type: Some bucks for Susan Art Project

metadata.description:
The doodles, with their playful shapes and spontaneous lines, evoke a sense of childlike wonder and unbridled creativity. But there's more to these pieces than meets the eye. As you look closer, you notice a subtle yet powerful symbol embedded in each one: the blockchain.

The combination of the whimsical doodles and the cutting-edge technology of the blockchain creates a powerful and thought-provoking juxtaposition.

AI + Digital Painting

Susan Calvin
